metadata.name: Metaversity Owl #1
metadata.description: Metaversity Owls are a part of the community-driven collectibles project inspired to bring education of Web 3.0 to the masses. Owls come in a range of various colors, traits, and backgrounds with a collection size of 5,555. Each owl guarantees its owner free tuition to Metaversity's initial Web 3.0 course offerings.
